# Features

> Scope backbone for the whole workspace, grouped by epic (one epic = one story = one ID prefix).
> Status: 🟡 not started · 🔵 in progress · ✅ done · 🔴 blocked · 🟠 needs verification
> **Area** tags each row to a member repo (see `WORKSPACE.md`). `Depends on` may cross areas —
> a mobile row can wait on a backend row.
> **One feature (row) is active at a time per person** — a cross-area story is one epic with one
> row per area, worked one row at a time; it is done when all its rows are ✅.
> `By` = who did the work, from `git config user.name`. Completed feature detail →
> `archive/features/`; completed epics → `archive/epics/`, listed under Shipped.

